(1, 1048586, 1, 1, '2017-01-16 16:35:05', '2017-01-16 16:35:05', '[JNSAMR] Copyediting Request', '<p>Test Copy Editor:<br> <br> I would ask that you undertake the copyediting of " Test paper 1" for Journal of the National Student Association for Medical Research by following these steps.<br> 1. Click on the Submission URL below.<br> 2. Open any files available under Draft Files and do your copyediting, while adding any Copyediting Discussions as needed.<br> 3. Save copyedited file(s), and upload to Copyedited panel.<br> 4. Notify the Editor that all files have been prepared, and that the Production process may begin.<br> <br> Journal of the National Student Association for Medical Research URL: <a href="http://www.nsamr.ac.uk/journal/journal-machinery/ojs-3.0.1/index.php/jnsamr">http://www.nsamr.ac.uk/journal/journal-machinery/ojs-3.0.1/index.php/jnsamr</a><br> Submission URL: <a href="http://www.nsamr.ac.uk/journal/journal-machinery/ojs-3.0.1/index.php/jnsamr/workflow/access/1">http://www.nsamr.ac.uk/journal/journal-machinery/ojs-3.0.1/index.php/jnsamr/workflow/access/1</a><br> Username: testcopyeditor<br> <br> JNSAMR Administration<br>it@nsamr.ac.uk</p><br/><br/>\n________________________________________________________________________<br/>\n<a href="http://www.nsamr.ac.uk/journal/journal-machinery/ojs-3.0.1/index.php/jnsamr">Journal of the National Student Association for Medical Research</a>'),
